data.title: Outpatient Clinic S3, Meilahti Bridge Hospital
data.meta_description: Meilahti Bridge Hospital Outpatient Clinic S3 admits patients by appointment only. Patients come to us for their first appointment with a referral, or for a postoperative check-up. We do not provide emergency services.
data.text:
Musculoskeletal and Plastic Surgery Outpatient Clinic is located at Meilahti Bridge Hospital Outpatient Clinic S3.

We treat patients in orthopedics and hand surgery.

On this page, it is possible to use the chatbot for Musculoskeletal and Plastic Surgery, which can answer frequently asked questions. If the bot is not able to answer your question, you can chat (in finnish) with a customer service representative. You can find the bot at the bottom right of the page.

You can use our online services by signing in to the Maisa Portal. Once your treatment with us begins, you will receive information on the services you can access in Maisa. These include appointment booking and preliminary information forms, for exam
